!!   Expected output
!!
!!##AUTHOR
!!   John S. Urban
!!
!!##REFERENCE
!!   The article "Matching Wildcards: An Empirical Way to Tame an Algorithm"
!!   in Dr Dobb's Journal, By Kirk J. Krauss, October 07, 2014
!!
!!##LICENSE
